2041978","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546048477,"updated_time":1546048477,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e黎拉曼一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，“黎拉曼，你又对别人说你证明哥猜了！”他不回答，对柜里说，“来碟糕丝，一瓶太太乐。”便排出九文大钱。他们又故意地高声嚷道，“你准是对别人说你证明哥猜了！”黎拉曼睁大眼睛说，“你怎么这样凭空污人清白……”“什么清白？我前天亲眼见你去何家论证，后又被赶了出来。”黎拉曼便涨红了脸，额上的青筋条条绽出，争辩道，“交流不能算……证明！……“交流“，数学家的事，能算证明么？”接连便是难懂的话，什么“拉格朗日”，什么“洛必达”之类，引得众人都哄笑起来，店内外充满了快活的空气。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561940950,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561940950","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546017770,"updated_time":1546017770,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e早上十点钟一个小孩想抓到一条鱼吃，觉得一小时时间去菜市场有点赶，于是花了半小时抽干了太平洋的水打退鲸鱼干翻白鲨，终于找到了一条小鲤鱼然后开开心心回家去了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561935867,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"361ec8b51e862bc58fd3538bec0b47d1","url_token":"wang-bo-15-53-35","name":"性感毛妹